REMINDER
Last ah enna paathom label and input tag vachi antha box create panratha pathi paathom

NOW
Antha mari create la panniduvom ana athula oru prblm iruku enna na entha input ku enna lebel nu theriyathu browser kum theriyathu athukaga namba MAPPING pannanum input and label la.

<label>email</label>
<input type = “email” />

<label>password</label>
<input type = “password” />

Ipdi irukum itha epdi mapping panrathu nu paakalam
ID and FOR intha two attributes use panni map panna porom

<label for = “email”>email</label>
<input type = “email” id = “email”/>

Intha mari than map pannanum id la enna kudukuromo athu than for laiyum kudukanum 
EXAMPLE

<label for = “password”>password</label>
<input type = “password” id = “password”/>

Ippo browser ku intha input ku intha label nu theriyum.

NEXT 
Ippo ithu oru form atha epdi create panrathu nu paathom nxt uh atha submit pannanum la athuku enna pannanum already know button use pannanum like

<button>submit</button>

Ipdi use pannuvoma ana ithu epdi use aaganum antha form la namba email and password kuduthu then submit pannanum epdi na

<label for = “email”>email</label>
<input type = “email” id = “email”/>
<label for = “password”>password</label>
<input type = “password” id = “password”/>
<button>submit</button>

Ipdi irukum but namba starting la irunthu enna paathom form la use panratha paathom but itha form ku epdi submit panrathu ethume illa ma rendu label , input and button create phantom so epdi form ku change pannanum na form tag ah use pannaum ithu ellathaiyum form tag la vaikanum 

<form>
        <label for = “email”>email</label>
        <input type = “email” id = “email”/>

        <label for = “password”>password</label>
        <input type = “password” id = “password”/>

        <button>submit</button>
</form>

